Class InventoryManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • InventoryManager
  • public class InventoryManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Entry point of the application for the user. In essence a utility class of with no instances. The InventoryManager class coordinates calls between the front end and back end elements of entire application. It includes methods for both inventory searches and execution of sales.
    Since:
    2021 - 07 - 25

      • RESTOCK_AMOUNT

        private static final int RESTOCK_AMOUNT
        A constant set to the desired target amount for item restocking. When automatic orders to restock are generated, RESTOCK_AMOUNT - (current item stock) is ordered.

      • searchName

        public static java.lang.Integer searchName​(java.lang.String itemName)
        Searches inventory for a Tool item by name. The item name must be a perfect characater-by-character match but does not need to match letter casing.
        Parameters:
        itemName - the name used to search inventory
        Returns:
        index of the Tool element within inventory with a matching item name. Returns null if no matches are found.
